"type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"See for example ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","type":"topic","title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"symbol"},"ic_layers.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","identifier":"ic_layers.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.png"}]},"https://system.design.orange.com/0c1af118d/p/2531b9-accessibility-compliance":{"identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","title":"the following guidelines","url":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"the following guidelines"}]},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"images":[{"identifier":"ic_layers.png","type":"icon"}],"